Santa_Cruz.Soquel, California:
Soquel  is a census-designated place (CDP) in Santa Cruz County, California, United States approximately 75 miles (120 km) south of San Francisco, and forms part of the north coast of Monterey Bay. The population was 9,644 at the 2010 census.


== Geography ==
Soquel is located at 36°59′13″N 121°56′44″W (36.986991, -121.945636).
